;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 503106001: Config/Level/Mission/5031060/Act/Act503106001.json-->
::'''Czipo:''' The music party's performance has ended, the instruments have been moved away, and the band members have all gone their separate ways. My heart is empty now.
::'''Czipo:''' I'll leave my precious memories here.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503106001_9-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503106001_9-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} But the other members are still here.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106004-->
:::'''Czipo:''' Miss Rappa left! She's the soul of The Dazzling! We can still meet up with the other members, but it still feels like something is missing.
:::'''Czipo:''' The passion for performing? The rowdy atmosphere? Or the courage to push ahead to perform despite the disapproval from the schools?
:::'''Czipo:''' *sigh* I can't really put it into words. It's just that... after the performance, going to all those parties feels dull.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} I thought you were gonna go learn some ninjutsu?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106008-->
:::'''Czipo:''' Learn ninjutsu? Hmm... Did I say that? I don't quite remember. Let me think. Let me think...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are Fortune Academy students all so capricious?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You're lying to me again!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106011-->
:::'''Czipo:''' Oh well, plans always change, and I have so many interests and hobbies. It's normal to switch to a different life goal.
:::'''Czipo:''' Yes! I remember now, I wanted to ask Miss Rappa to teach me ninjutsu! To tell you the truth, after the show ended, I learned plenty of fundamentals from Miss Rappa, even though they were excruciatingly hard.
:::'''Czipo:''' What's all this nonsense about ninja talisman drawing techniques, ninja mantra chant cadence, super ninja dynamic vision training... They're even more tiring than my private gym lessons! I want to become a Ninja Hero! Not to feel like dying all the time!
:::'''Czipo:''' That's why I gave up. There are all kinds of *heroes* all around the world. It won't make a difference without me.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} So what's next for you?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106016-->
:::'''Czipo:''' {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} Manager, you've asked a great question. I've been troubled over this recently too.
:::'''Czipo:''' It's almost time for graduation, but I haven't thought of what to do next. Do I find a decent job, stay in school for further education, or... become an independent musician?
:::'''Czipo:''' We've gone through so much together. We know each other well. In your eyes, what do you think I'm most suitable for?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503106001_29-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503106001_29-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Go to work!
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106020-->
::::'''Czipo:''' I'd also like to venture into the workforce, but... as you know, it's difficult to land a job now, much less get a relaxing job with easy money. And I don't want to leave Penacony... It's a hassle.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} It's better to further your studies.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106022-->
::::'''Czipo:''' My teacher gave me the same advice and even said it would be a waste if I didn't become his student. But somehow I feel... he just hopes that I stay in school so I can help him with his stuff. He can order me around without even paying me a wage.
::::'''Czipo:''' No can do. I've never had much interest in academia. I would be wasting my life away if I stayed on.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} I think you do have musical talent.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106025-->
::::'''Czipo:''' ...Really? I think so too! From the moment I stood on stage, I knew I wanted to give my life to music!
::::'''Czipo:''' But... to turn my interest into a job... is it too idealistic? What if I don't become popular? What if I can't earn any money or even sell any tickets? Just thinking about this makes me afraid.
::::'''Czipo:''' Then, should I just forget about it and look for a job?
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...You best decide for yourself.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106029-->
::::'''Czipo:''' It's too difficult. I can't think of an answer.
::::'''Czipo:''' *sigh* Forget it. I shall not worry anymore. I better quickly get my graduation certificate and return home to take over the family business.
::::'''Czipo:''' Since I can't find the right direction, that means that none of the paths are suitable for me. If l can choose an easy mode for life, I shouldn't make it any harder than it needs to be.
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Then why did you even ask me?
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Doesn't this mean you never had any troubles to begin with?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106034-->
::::'''Czipo:''' Facing important life decisions can be quite overwhelming. After all, taking over the family business does involve a lot of things too.
::::'''Czipo:''' Thank you for helping me with my career analysis, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} Manager!
::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
