::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_503106116-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106116-->
::'''Czipo:''' Let me see... That's amazing, it suits me so well! No wonder you're our {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} Manager! You've made my page stand out with just a few sentences!
::'''Czipo:''' Oh yeah, I've made you a copy, so you don't have to wait for the yearbook to be published. Don't forget me!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
