:{{DIcon|Hand}} Can I touch the fluff ball on your head?
::'''Czipo:''' ...Is this some new pick-up tactic? Why didn't I hear about this at a party?
::'''Czipo:''' If you're interested... Of course you can! We're so familiar with each other, it's normal to show some affection. Come, try it, this is a good opportunity to deepen our trust!
::After a moment's hesitation, you lightly place your finger on the white fluff ball. From that soft touch, you are certain that the awkwardness from that rude question just now was worth it. You are very willing to risk your skin for that experience again.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Bro, your fluff ball feels nice.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You're really nice.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106286-->
::'''Czipo:''' Heh-heh, it's an honor to make {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} Manager this happy!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404035602-->)
:{{DIcon}} I want to chat with you.
::'''Czipo:''' You're too polite, {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} Manager! We are so familiar with each other, just speak freely!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503106004_80-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503106004_80-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Will you still keep in contact with the other band members?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106203-->
:::'''Czipo:''' Of course. We are comrades that stood by each other through thick and thin. Our trust in each other is unshakable. This deep-rooted friendship can't be compared to those fair-weather friends you meet at parties!
:::'''Czipo:''' We'll meet regularly and chat about school, update each other on what's going on recently, and discuss future plans... *sigh* But with Miss Rappa's departure, it feels like something is missing whenever we meet.
:::'''Czipo:''' ...The Dazzling will not disband, but she is the lead of our band.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Is Fortune Academy still giving you a hard time?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106207-->
:::'''Czipo:''' Haha, speaking of this, ever since The Dazzling chased away that unscrupulous academy representative, my standing in the academy has soared. All my classmates and teachers greatly respect me now.
:::'''Czipo:''' He brought it on himself. Many students already disliked him, so now they finally can get back at him.
:::'''Czipo:''' Now, I'm the hero of Fortune Academy &mdash; Master Ninja Czipo! Hahahaha!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} That's all the questions I have.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503106211-->
:::'''Czipo:''' If you ever want to chat, do look for me anytime!
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404035602-->)
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Enjoy this music party to the fullest!
::'''Czipo:''' I will! I must treasure the final moments of joy before graduation &mdash; viva la music party! Viva la music!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
